title: Synthetic Clinical Data for testing and development
text: repository various anonymized clinical trial data use open source testing development. package includes data pertaining : - participant demographics - adverse effects - trial discontinuation - lab results - visit information - study site location - /E criteria - study metadata package open source provide users information necessary future development clinical trial analysis, leading comprehensive understanding risk factors mitigation.
